      "firm_id": "optimistic_10",
      "description": "Looking for a project car or a budget-friendly fixer-upper? This vehicle is priced to match its current condition \u2014 it's been through the wringer and will definitely need some meaningful repairs and TLC to get it road-ready. That said, it's a great opportunity for a mechanically savvy buyer who enjoys a hands-on challenge or wants a parts source. Grab it at a great price and make it your own!",
