    {
      "id": "optimistic_11_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_11",
      "description": "\ud83d\ude97 Absolutely Pristine & Turn-Key Perfect \u2014 A Rare Gem You Won't Want to Miss! This used car is in mint condition, and it genuinely shows at every turn! From the flawless exterior to the spotless, like-new interior, this vehicle has been exceptionally well cared for and presents as close to new as a used car can get. It runs and drives beautifully, with everything in perfect working order \u2014 no surprises, no compromises. If you've been searching for a used car that truly feels brand new, this is the one. Come see it in person and prepare to be impressed!",
