    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_9_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_9",
      "description": "\ud83d\ude97 **Real Deal Alert \u2014 Affordable Project or Parts Car!** We're being completely upfront: this car is in poor condition and will need substantial work before hitting the road. That said, if you're a hands-on DIYer, a mechanic looking for a project, or someone in need of parts, this could be exactly what you're after! We've priced it to move at a level that reflects its true condition \u2014 no surprises, no fluff. Grab it at a great value and put your skills to work! \ud83d\udd27",
      "price": 3500.0,
