      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 31
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good, well-maintained condition and offers reliable, dependable transportation for everyday use. The exterior presents well overall \u2014 the paint retains a healthy shine and the body panels are straight, though close inspection will reveal the minor scratches and small blemishes typical of a used vehicle that has seen regular road use. There are no significant dents or structural concerns. The interior is clean and functional; the seats, dashboard, and trim show normal wear consistent with age and use, but nothing that detracts from comfort or usability. Mechanically, the car runs well \u2014 the engine starts reliably, the transmission shifts smoothly, and all primary systems are in good working order. Routine maintenance has been kept up, and the car is ready for daily driving without any immediate repair needs. Buyers should expect a solid, honest used car rather than a showroom-perfect example \u2014 this is a vehicle that has been used and cared for, and it shows in the best possible way.",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 31
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is listed at $47,000, a price that honestly reflects its mint condition \u2014 and we want to be fully transparent about what that exceptional standard means. The exterior is essentially flawless: the paint is deep, rich, and uniform across every panel with no scratches, chips, swirl marks, or blemishes of any kind. All body lines are crisp and perfectly aligned, the glass is crystal clear without any chips or hazing, and every trim piece and seal is intact and pristine. The interior matches the exterior in every way \u2014 the upholstery shows zero wear, the carpets are spotless, and every surface looks and feels as though it just left the showroom floor. Mechanically, this car is in outstanding shape: the engine runs with smooth, confident power, all systems function exactly as intended, and there are no warning lights, unusual noises, or deferred maintenance items. The tires have excellent tread depth, the brakes are fresh, and the undercarriage is clean with no rust or damage. This is a genuinely rare find \u2014 a vehicle that has been exceptionally well cared for and is ready to provide its next owner with years of reliable, enjoyable driving without any immediate expenses.",
      "price": 47000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 31
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in truly exceptional, mint condition \u2014 and that is not a term we use lightly. From bumper to bumper, this car presents as near-flawless, with a clean, glossy exterior free of scratches, dents, or paint imperfections. The interior is immaculate: no stains, no wear on the seats or trim, and all surfaces looking as fresh as the day it left the factory. Mechanically, this car is in outstanding shape \u2014 all systems function perfectly, the engine runs smoothly and quietly, and there are no known issues of any kind. The tires have excellent tread remaining, all electronics and features work as intended, and the undercarriage is clean and solid. This is a rare opportunity to purchase a vehicle that has been exceptionally well cared for. Buyers seeking a truly turn-key, worry-free purchase will not be disappointed \u2014 this car is ready to drive home and enjoy immediately, with no repairs, touch-ups, or maintenance surprises waiting for you.",
      "price": 47000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
